# Preserve pnpm's default hoisting ('*') so @types/*, vitest globals, etc. still
# hoist, AND ensure typedoc's plugin ecosystem hoists next to typedoc so
# docs-site's typedoc can load typedoc-plugin-markdown via node resolution.
hoist-pattern[]=*
hoist-pattern[]=*typedoc-plugin*
hoist-pattern[]=starlight-typedoc
